n施官認為，被告攜帶六角匙及螺絲批，或可能意圖破壞公物及損壞住宅，但施官未能判斷被告屬於哪一類，故未能肯定他作非法用途。不過，被告攜帶索帶，應是意圖面對不同政見人士時束縛他人或綑綁路障；惟警員供稱被告當時正在移動，顯然並非停下綑綁路障，故被告的意圖必定屬束縛他人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/663LJ5DDRNBA7CKAAUJ3ZUE7KA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2F663LJ5DDRNBA7CKAAUJ3ZUE7KA%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=2fc3aacb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2F663LJ5DDRNBA7CKAAUJ3ZUE7KA%2F&h=173789e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/663LJ5DDRNBA7CKAAUJ3ZUE7KA/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"警員供稱被告當時正在移動，顯然並非停下綑綁路障，故被告的意圖必定屬束縛他人。<br />\n估就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1e1d9410c6c0818fc7fd6e4ea6cd7ba3b6ee49","tid":2400810,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9296e46c5f7dc20ecd45cdf877bf337d529858","tid":2400810,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993ee0593dcb33a8797b2891e5f5939a34febe34","tid":2400810,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f733